videos.description: Josh Jackson tosses it up to Henri Murphy down the sideline and Murphy climbs the ladder in the face of a defender to make the impressive catch.
videos.headline: Hokies pick up 24 with one-handed grab

videos.description: Josh Jackson keeps it on the option and pounds his way in for the 13-yard score.
videos.headline: Jackson puts Hokies on board first with TD

videos.description: Josh Jackson botches the exchange on the 1-yard line and the loose ball is scooped up by Ramon Richards.
videos.headline: Hokies turn it over on the 1-yard line

videos.description: Mason Rudolph launches a pass down the sideline to  Marcell Ateman who hauls in the catch and is wrestled down on the 1-yard line.
videos.headline: Cowboys get into red zone after 50-yard toss

videos.description: Justice Hill follows up the long pass with a touchdown run to give the Cowboys the lead.
videos.headline: Hill puts Cowboys up with rushing TD

videos.description: Mason Rudolph throws a ball to the corner of the end zone and connects with a sliding Dillon Stoner for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Rudolph throws TD to extend Cowboys' lead

videos.description: Josh Jackson throws a laser in to the end zone and Eric Kumah rips the ball away from the Cowboys for the Virginia Tech touchdown.
videos.headline: Hokies answer with strong TD grab

videos.description: Mason Rudolph sees James Washington breaking away from his defender and connects for a 65-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Rudolph launches 2nd passing TD

videos.description: Case Mummau dials up his inner Josh Jackson and finds Anthony Shegog for a 22-yard gain on the fake punt.
videos.headline: Perfectly executed fake punt leads to VT first down

videos.description: Josh Jackson's pass goes through the hands of Phil Patterson and into the arms of Oklahoma State's Darius Curry.
videos.headline: Cowboys intercept deflected pass

videos.description: Josh Jackson sneaks up the middle and stretches his body over the goal line for the touchdown to get Virginia Tech within 6.
videos.headline: Jackson stretches for TD to make it a 1-score game

videos.description: Oklahoma State defeats Virginia Tech in the Camping World Bowl and head coach Mike Gundy gets drenched with the Gatorade bath.
videos.headline: Gundy bathes in Gatorade after bowl win

videos.description: Oklahoma State quarterback Mason Rudolph is going to miss Coach Gundy and his "weapons" on offense as he moves on to the NFL.
videos.headline: Rudolph: 'It's good to end on a high note'

videos.description: After a performance of 351 passing yards and 2 touchdowns, Mason Rudolph is named Camping World Bowl MVP.
videos.headline: Mason Rudolph takes home MVP

videos.description: Oklahoma State defeats Virginia Tech 30-21 in the Camping World Bowl and Coach Gundy credits the Cowboy fan base for a great season.
videos.headline: Cowboys hoist the Camping World Bowl trophy

videos.description: Mason Rudolph throws for 351 yards and 2 touchdowns as the Cowboys take down the Hokies.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State defeats Virginia Tech in the Camping World Bowl

videos.description: Oklahoma State head coach Mike Gundy joins SVP and gives his quarterback Mason Rudolph high praise.
